snippet.title: Raji: an Ancient Epic - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Raji: an Ancient Epic is coming out on PC, Xbox and PlayStation on October 15th!

Wishlist the game on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/730390/Raji_An_Ancient_Epic/

Raji: An Ancient Epic is an action-adventure game taking place in Ancient India. Raji, a young girl is chosen by the gods, to stand against the demonic invasion of the human realm. Her destiny is to rescue her younger brother and face the demon lord Mahabalasura.

For more on Raji: An Ancient Epic, follow the game on social media on the following channels.

► Visit our official page https://www.rajithegame.com/
